*Unlock Faster Warehouse Inwarding*




We=E2=80=99re bringing warehouse inwarding workflows directly into the Dash=
board to
better support daily operations and ensure end-to-end process continuity,
ensuring undelivered orders are received, verified, and processed smoothly.


To better support this workflow, we=E2=80=99re extending *inwarding capabil=
ities
directly from the Dashboard*=E2=80=94making it easier for warehouse teams t=
o
complete key actions from the tool they rely on most.
Why this matters?



Warehouse admins play a key role in receiving orders from riders and
ensuring they are verified and processed smoothly as part of daily
operations. However, the inwarding action is currently available only on
the Admin App, which can require additional switching between tools to
complete these workflows efficiently.
[image: image placeholder]


What=E2=80=99s in it for you!



This update is designed to make warehouse workflows simpler, clearer, and
more reliable:

   -

   *Seamless Rider --> Warehouse Handshakes*
   Ensure every order handover is acknowledged digitally and accurately.
   -

   *Reduced Manual Effort*
   Move away from offline confirmations and manual tracking.
   -

   *Better Reconciliation*
   Lower chances of mismatches and post-processing errors.
   -

   *Smoother Warehouse Operations*
   Complete inwarding actions without switching platforms.




What=E2=80=99s new?

   -

   *Bulk Inwarding for Rider Handovers*
   Warehouse admins can now inward multiple orders at once for a single
   rider directly from the Dashboard.
   -

   *Faster Inwarding*
   No more inwarding one order at a time=E2=80=94complete rider handovers i=
n bulk
   with just a few clicks.
   -

   *Smoother Warehouse Flow*
   Streamline high-volume inbound operations with a quicker, more reliable
   inwarding experience.

That's It!


This enhancement brings greater clarity and efficiency to warehouse
workflows=E2=80=94right where your teams already work.
